WEBVTT

00:00:07.440 --> 00:00:10.080
Hûn çawa dizanin ku hûn birastî hene?

00:00:10.087 --> 00:00:12.932
Heta mirov li ser nefikire 
pirs hesan xuya dike.

00:00:12.956 --> 00:00:14.661
Haydê em li bersivê bigerin.

00:00:14.685 --> 00:00:17.159
Hûn çawa dizanin ku hûn birastî hene?

00:00:17.159 --> 00:00:19.873
Di pirtûka
"Meditations on First Philosophy,"

00:00:19.873 --> 00:00:23.018
René Descartes 
hewil dike bersiv bide gelek pirsan.

00:00:23.042 --> 00:00:26.340
Hemû raman û mefhûmê kevin radike,

00:00:26.340 --> 00:00:28.960
ji serî dest pê dike.

00:00:28.987 --> 00:00:32.272
Hemû zanyariyen tên, ji hîsên tê tên.